Feature: Catalog Status
	In order to quickly and easily manage my catalog of movies
	As a movie owner
	I want to determine the status of my movie catalog

Scenario: Add a couple movies and validate the size of the catalog
	Given: That I want to quickly and easily manage my catalog of movies
	When: I add 2 movies to the catalog
	Then: I will have 2 movies in the catalog
	
Scenario: Add no movies and validate the size of the catalog remains zero
	Given: That I want to quickly and easily manage my catalog of movies
	When: I add 0 movies to the catalog
	Then: I will 0 movies in the catalog